metadata.name: DO NOT MINT THIS SHIT
metadata.description:
This is pretty self explanatory but since you're still reading for some reason I guess I need to tell you again so here goes:

DO NOT  
MINT  
THIS  
SHIT

Are we clear now? Ok good...

Seriously why are you still reading this? Do I need to say it again!?  
I'm not sure how I can make myself any clearer...

If you made it this far then I guess it's a good time for me to tell you the true ambitions of this project. You see I wanted something that explicitly told you not to mint so that I could actually... secretly... hide the true message. That message being:


DO NOT  
MINT  
THIS  
SHIT

BOZO
